                     Language War Command Summary
                     ============================
 COMMANDS
 --------
 d1              move in direction d1 (d1 = 1 to 8) 
 w s             set warp speed (s = 0 to 5)  
 p e d1 d2       shoot e-hundred unit phasor in direction d1.d2 (e = 0 to 9)  
 t d1 d2         shoot torpedo in direction d1.d2
 a d1 d2         shoot antimatter pod in direction d1.d2 
		 Press Enter to detonate.
 g               display / cancel galaxy scan
 $               abandon the Euphoria for the Assembler shuttlecraft
 x               cancel a partially entered command
 !               pause the game - hit 'x' to resume
 Esc             abort the game

